flowchart TD
    A[User opens FlashMarket] --> B{Logged in?}
    B -- No --> C[/guest route]
    B -- Yes --> D[/ main marketplace]

    C --> E[Browse live items as guest]
    E --> F[Click Sign in with Google]
    F --> G[Supabase Google OAuth]
    G --> H[/auth/callback]
    H --> I{Profile exists?}
    I -- No --> J[/auth/role]
    I -- Yes --> D

    J --> K{Choose role}
    K -- Buyer --> L[Save buyer profile]
    K -- Vendor --> M[Enter shop name]
    M --> N[Enter base latitude and longitude]
    N --> O[Preview base location on map]
    O --> P[Save vendor profile to Supabase]
    L --> D
    P --> Q[/vendor dashboard]

    D --> R[Fetch items from /api/items]
    R --> S[Show dynamic pricing cards]
    S --> T[Buyer clicks Claim]
    T --> U[Open claim modal]
    U --> V{Pickup or Delivery?}
    V -- Pickup --> W[POST /api/items/[itemId]/claim]
    V -- Delivery --> X[Calculate distance and fee]
    X --> W
    W --> Y[Create claim in Supabase]
    Y --> Z[Update item quantity/status]
    Z --> AA{Delivery selected?}
    AA -- No --> AB[Claim complete]
    AA -- Yes --> AC[Create delivery task]
    AC --> AD[Delivery appears on /deliveries map]

    Q --> AE[Vendor adds listing]
    AE --> AF[POST /api/items]
    AF --> AG[Item stored in Supabase]
    AG --> AH[Appears in marketplace]

    AD --> AI[Nearby user claims delivery]
    AI --> AJ[Delivery status updated]
    AJ --> AK[Credits rewarded on completion]
